def get_now_time():
    # E/span>
    now_time = datetime.datetime.now(pytz.timezone('Asia/Tokyo'))
    return now_time

def is_dst(time):
    # 
    ny_time = time.astimezone(pytz.timezone('America/New_York'))
    # DSTEE/span>
    return ny_time.dst() != datetime.timedelta(0)

now_time = get_now_time()
print(f"Now time: {now_time}")

if is_dst(now_time):
    gosa = 6
    print(now_time, "mt5",gosa)
else:
    gosa = 7
    print(now_time,"mt5",gosa)

def byosha(df,jiku_col, txt_):
    x = df[jiku_col]

    # EE/span>
    fig, ax1 = plt.subplots(figsize=(size1, size2))

    # E/span>
    ax1.set_facecolor('#2a313c')  # 
    fig.patch.set_facecolor('#2a313c')  # EE

    # yE
    colors = ['r' if p < 0 else 'g' for p in df['profit']]
    ax1.bar(x, df['profit'], label='profit', color=colors, alpha=0.5)
    ax1.set_xlabel(jiku_col, color='#DDDDDD')  # 
    ax1.set_ylabel('Profit', color='#DDDDDD')
    ax1.tick_params(axis='both', colors='#DDDDDD')

    # E/span>
    plt.xticks(rotation=90, color='#DDDDDD')

    # EyE
    ax2 = ax1.twinx()
    ax2.plot(x, df['ken'], label='ken', color='b', marker='o')
    ax2.set_ylabel('Ken', color='#DDDDDD')
    ax2.tick_params(axis='both', colors='#DDDDDD')

    formatter = FuncFormatter(lambda x, _: '{:,.0f}'.format(x))
    ax1.yaxis.set_major_formatter(formatter)
    ax2.yaxis.set_major_formatter(formatter)
    # EE/span>
    plt.title(txt_, color='#DDDDDD')
    fig.tight_layout()

    # 
    plt.show()
